- An abstract method of looping with arrays:
  def output_array_elements(array)
   counter = 0
 
    while array[counter] do
      puts array[counter]
      counter += 1
   end
  end
  
- Theres also using the array.length or .size method:
  def output_array_elements(array)
    counter = 0
 
    while counter < array.length do
      puts array[counter]
      counter += 1
    end
  end
  